+"ayu_IntelGramUpdateLogCurrent" = "**Vault, timeline, automation, and private exports**\n- Universal local full-text search covers messages, filenames, media types, and links already received by IntelGram, with a unified view across signed-in accounts.\n- Timeline tools add jump-to-date, compact media history, conversation statistics, saved moments, and locally observed edit and deletion history.\n- Smart folders organize unread people, work, high-priority, needs-reply, and spam-review items.\n- Private contact notes retain context history and due reminders; opt-in identity snapshots record only public names, usernames, badges, and shared-group counts visible to this client.\n- Local rules can match keywords, links, photos, or files to tag, save, alert, mute, flag spam, or open Telegram's native forward picker for a confirmed ordinary-message queue.\n- Theme Studio includes real Windows 93, Terminal, Classic Telegram, and AMOLED packs, custom theme import, and IntelGram icon choices.\n- Export Center creates chat or account HTML, PDF, Markdown, JSON, and ZIP archives. Frozen Account Backup streams the full set and permitted downloaded files into one AES-256-GCM encrypted archive without leaving plaintext exports behind.\n- Per-chat tools add tags, priority, manual/Wi-Fi/always download modes, local read reminders, local-only drafts, and local notification muting.\n- Telegram's protected-content and self-destruct restrictions are enforced throughout the vault, rules, exports, and legacy local save paths.";
+"ayu_IntelGramUpdateLogFeaturesTitle" = "Main IntelGram features";
+"ayu_IntelGramUpdateLogFeatures" = "**Local profile and collectibles**\n- Display name, UID, primary and other usernames, anonymous number, bio, profile photo, badges, emoji status, and personal channel rendering.\n- Local profile cloning from a user already visible to IntelGram, plus cached lookup by UID or a phone number visible to your account.\n- Native collectible collection galleries, one featured collectible, up to six pinned collectibles, and local owner/profile rendering.\n\n**Private productivity**\n- Universal message vault, unified account inbox, timeline tools, edit/deletion history, smart folders, contact notes with reminders and history, identity inspector, local rules, anti-spam review, and per-chat controls.\n- Real Windows 93, Terminal, Classic Telegram, and AMOLED themes plus icon swapping.\n- Local HTML, PDF, Markdown, JSON, ZIP, and encrypted Frozen Account Backup exports with permitted cached media.";
+"ayu_IntelGramUpdateLogPrivacyTitle" = "Local-only boundary";
+"ayu_IntelGramUpdateLogPrivacy" = "Local profile tools never update your Telegram profile, import contacts, change collectible ownership, or join a channel automatically. Vault tools only process data already received by this client. Restrict Saving Content and self-destructing media are preserved: IntelGram stores a jump-back reference and basic metadata, never the protected body or media.";
+"ayu_IntelGramUpdateLogCredit" = "IntelGram local profile tools by fool.";
+"ayu_IntelGramUpdateLogFull" = "View full changelog";
